anji 的 AZKi、Luna Himemori 和 Akari Shishido，他也与 Kokoro Amamiya 合作。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="秋星！！萝莉神安魂曲☆ / 天音彼方 × 天宫心 × AZKi × 孺户明里 × 姬森露娜 (封面)" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/shXDiB3CZ60?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="4vqK7IGxxa"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/is-the-slanderer-of-hoshimachi-suisei-a-moderator-of-nijisanji-vtuber-amamiya-kokoro/">星町水成的诽谤者已成为二十三寺旗下 VTuber 雨宫心的可能版主。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“水星星町的诽谤者：出现了成为二十三寺的VTuber天宫心的版主的可能性” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/is-the-slanderer-of-hoshimachi-suisei-a-moderator-of-nijisanji-vtuber-amamiya-kokoro/embed/#?secret=RqeMIRVfnu#?secret=4vqK7IGxxa" data-secret="4vqK7IGxxa" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="0dUXCldbU9"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/slanderer-against-hoshimachi-suisei-overlapping-with-some-listeners-of-vtuber-group-nijisanji/">星町水成VTuber组合“虹三路”的诽谤 有报道称部分观众重叠</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“水成星町的诽谤者：有报道称，VTuber 团体“Nijisanji”的部分观众重叠” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/slanderer-against-hoshimachi-suisei-overlapping-with-some-listeners-